---
import Link from "./ui/link.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="relative mt-32 mb-16 mx-auto max-w-5xl">
  <!-- Soft glowing aura behind the card -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand/10 rounded-[3rem] blur-3xl animate-slow-spin -z-10"></div>
  
  <div class="relative group bg-white/80 p-12 md:px-24 md:py-24 rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col items-center text-center border border-brand-border/30 overflow-hidden shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] backdrop-blur-xl hover-lift transition-all duration-500">
    
    <!-- Light subtle gradient background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-text bg-brand-soft/80 border border-brand-border/40 rounded-full mb-8 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm">
        <Icon class="w-4 h-4 text-brand" name="bx:bxs-zap" />
        推荐先 Fork，再部署到自己的 Cloudflare
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight max-w-4xl text-slate-900 drop-shadow-sm">
        从核心仓库开始，部署一个属于自己的 EdgeEver
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-slate-600 mt-8 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        核心项目已经提供 <code class="bg-slate-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">deploy:setup</code>、<code class="bg-slate-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">deploy:doctor</code> 和 <code class="bg-slate-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">deploy</code> 三段式部署命令。使用 AI Agent 时，也可以把 Fork 仓库链接交给 Agent 自动部署。
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 mt-12 w-full justify-center">
        <Link 
          href="https://github.com/msh01/edgeever" 
          target="_blank" 
          size="lg"
          class="flex gap-2 items-center justify-center font-bold bg-slate-900 text-white hover:bg-slate-800 shadow-xl transition-all hover:scale-105 rounded-xl px-8 py-4 border border-slate-800">
          <Icon class="w-6 h-6" name="bx:bxl-github" />
          打开 EdgeEver 仓库
        </Link>
        <a 
          href="https://github.com/msh01/edgeever/blob/main/docs/agent-deploy-cloudflare.md" 
          target="_blank"
          class="flex gap-2 items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white/80 border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-xl text-slate-700 hover:text-slate-900 transition-all font-semibold backdrop-blur-lg shadow-sm">
          <Icon class="w-5 h-5 text-brand" name="bx:bxs-bot" />
          查看 AI 助理部署协议
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
